{"tid":140193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"23歲仔失蹤3日 曾返深圳箍牙","createTime":"2017-03-02T04:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T05:45:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d92a34af9ec07d0bf6b45bdfcf16e124838a608e","tid":140193,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:18:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170302/19945112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170302%2F19945112&d=DXsCe6mrroMB06wP0eqGVWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=1d922677\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170302%2F19945112&h=cd360b68\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170302/19945112</a><br />\n<br />\n23歲仔失蹤3日<br />\n曾返深圳箍牙<br />\n<br />\n9,756<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】23歲青年張文俊，星期一早上6點半在大圍一間車房工作至半途，突然拖篋離開，一直失蹤至今，其家人感到擔憂，昨凌晨時分抵田心警署報案，下午再在fb發相尋人，希望巿民提供有關他的消息。<br />\n<br />\n張文俊身高1.7米，120磅重，瘦身材束黑色短髮，身上有身份證、回鄉證、$1000人民幣及少量港幣，失蹤前穿着藍色外套。<br />\n<br />\n俊仔胞兄表示，弟弟中學畢業後跟隨家人在車房工作，失蹤前並無異樣，身體一直健康亦無病痛，惟獨不知他的感情狀況，他失蹤前一晚到深圳會見牙醫箍牙，之後再返家睡覺，但翌日早上返回大圍車房後突然出走。家人不知其去向，曾托他的朋友向俊仔發WhatsApp及微信查問，均未獲回覆，擔心他會出事，現希望他有何問題，能回家與家人商量，「希望細佬睇到篇文章，盡快覆返屋企人，起碼報番個平安，想知佢人有冇事，安唔安全」。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n不滿被炒魷？男子4度虛報燒酒樓<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n建制議員促釋放暴力七警　黎棟國：政治特赦無先例"},{"pid":"776a562009ed24295add6eee02ff40f7c84e692f","tid":140193,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170302/org/1488398547_146e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170302%2Forg%2F1488398547_146e.jpg&h=f505d337&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aca7df592feb111b412c0ca86c36b536e1ca1e63","tid":140193,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:23:19.000Z","msg":"15日後可能先返到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4b44c13ffcedf3fbc8c649a3742c875dce2bf8","tid":140193,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"返黎唔見左個腎"},{"pid":"6c1c5cb2bab3947869797c09a8194a00c37a7c07","tid":140193,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d45aa72092240d61a51b5f6983355cdba655c2f","tid":140193,"uid":87971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:29:00.000Z","msg":"頭先睇fb 好似搵番"},{"pid":"9043877fcd3ef424391fc4bb088de66e7dce8afe","tid":140193,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>15日後可能先返到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行政拘留<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ba6103230875237a17500ebe724bb2750bf835","tid":140193,"uid":37231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"可能叫雞唔想比人知啫<br />\n有咩消息叫我一聲"},{"pid":"46763e4dadfb5946850d98cbd813f1d831ad2d61","tid":140193,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"應該比人活摘左大部分器官<br />\n<br />\n兇多吉少架啦"},{"pid":"561a18296b398e0e72633243e0ac2baaf53205c1","tid":140193,"uid":59705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>15日後可能先返到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgm